## Done criteria for this repo

Do not consider the task done until all of the following are true:

- the exact-size desktop screenshot has been captured
- the screenshot diff (or equivalent side-by-side check) has been reviewed
- typography has been checked at the reference width
- iconography completeness has been checked
- supplied assets have been used or accurately replaced with placeholders/generated assets
- the page builds/runs with the standard repo commands
